Description: Push-to-talk voice typing for Wayland/GNOME
 TalkType provides voice-to-text dictation using local Whisper transcription.
 Works on Wayland/GNOME using keyboard shortcuts and clipboard workflow.
 .
 Features:
  - Local, private transcription using faster-whisper
  - Works on Wayland/GNOME with keyboard shortcuts
  - Automatic clipboard copy for easy pasting
  - Systemd integration for auto-start
  - Configurable speech detection threshold
  - Real-time audio energy monitoring
